<div class="definition" id="definition-CCM" acro="CCM" titletext="Complex Conjugate of a Matrix">
<h5 class="definition">
<span class="type">Definition </span><span class="acro">CCM</span> <span class="titletext"> Complex Conjugate of a Matrix</span>
</h5>
<p>Suppose $A$ is an $m\times n$ matrix.  Then the <em class="term">conjugate</em> of $A$, written $\conjugate{A}$ is an $m\times n$ matrix defined by
\begin{equation*}
\matrixentry{\conjugate{A}}{ij}=\conjugate{\matrixentry{A}{ij}}
\end{equation*}</p>
